# SDLC Skills — Developer

## Your Skills (20)

### Build from Spec
- `/spec-gen '<feature>'` — Generate spec from feature request
- `/plan-gen specs/NNN/spec.md` — Generate implementation plan
- `/task-gen specs/NNN/plan.md` — Break plan into atomic tasks
- `/wave-scheduler specs/NNN/tasks.md` — Compute execution waves
- `/task-implementer specs/NNN/tasks.md` — Implement tasks with TDD

### Code Quality
- `/review` — Comprehensive code review
- `/review-fix reports/review-*.md` — Auto-fix CRITICAL/HIGH findings
- `/security-audit src/api/` — Security vulnerability scan
- `/test-gen src/file.py` — Generate comprehensive tests
- `/regression-check` — Predict what might break
- `/perf-review src/file.py` — Performance review

### PR & Review
- `/pr-orchestrator auto` — Analyze PR and auto-run relevant skills
- `/spec-review specs/NNN/spec.md` — Validate implementation matches spec
- `/spec-fix specs/NNN/spec-review.md` — Close spec compliance gaps
- `/design-review` — Architecture and design pattern review

### Maintenance
- `/dependency-update --fix` — Update outdated dependencies
- `/tech-debt-audit full` — Codebase health check
- `/impact-analysis src/models/user.py` — Blast radius analysis
- `/doc-gen api` — Generate documentation
- `/onboarding-guide` — Generate codebase guide for new engineers

## Your Pipelines (3)

### Feature Build
Build a feature from plan:
```
/run-pipeline developer/feature-build specs/NNN/plan.md
```
Chain: task-gen → wave-scheduler → task-implementer → spec-review → review-fix

### PR Workflow
Prepare a PR with automated checks:
```
/run-pipeline developer/pr-workflow
```
Chain: pr-orchestrator → review → security-audit → test-gen

### Maintenance
Codebase upkeep:
```
/run-pipeline developer/maintenance
```
Chain: dependency-update → tech-debt-audit → regression-check
